snippet.title: Wake Up Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Wake Up for FREE on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com//app/499540

Wake Up will let you experience a mysterious dream in Virtual Reality, where your only guide is a small butterfly.
Can you solve the riddles and manage to wake up?

Key Features:

 * A very diverse set of riddles
 * An interesting set of environments
 * A handcrafted sound experience
 * Designed specifically for VR and Motion Controllers
